{
  "stem": "27759.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the white soldiers, they took a lot of their prejudice over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would tell the Englishman that we were monkeys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that they'd go out at night, said we had a tail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would be swaying through the trees with our tail.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so one incident, this-- he was a corporal, and I had gone to town and passed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this English girl ask him to see his tail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until he says, you want to see my tail?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he unbuckled his belt and dropped his pants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Plus his undergarment.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then he said, now you see my tail?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, no, I don't see no tail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, well you asked to see my tail, that's the only tail I got.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the white MPs, they arrested him and brought him back to camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a colonel there in charge of that outfit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told me, he said you take this soldier back to town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told the black soldier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, now, if they ask to see your tail again, you do the same exact thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Show them your tail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they had spread-- the white soldiers had spread all sorts of rumors about us to the Englishmen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of them were unintelligent enough to believe these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you take some intelligent people, a lot of intelligent people in England, and they didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took it with a grain of salt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just ignored it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But those are some of the things I encountered in England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Southampton.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right on the Channel, the English Channel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as far as you could see, there was nothing but soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soldiers getting ready to cross the English Channel into France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
